reviewText: This movie is a childhood favorite, it did not matter that the instructions to play it were in polish. What matters is that it did not work. I had no intentions of requesting my money back, I just did not won't you to get any other persons hopes up ( no matter what nationality). So no I will not change my feedback score, and feel free to take the money back!!!!!
It was in a format I was not able to view with my DVD player.
